StmtSimple.StatementText: SELECT count(*) FROM category as cat JOIN subcategory as sub ON sub.category_id = cat.id JOIN product as prod ON prod.subcategory_id = sub.id JOIN order_details as ord_det ON ord_det.product_id = prod.id JOIN [order] as ord ON ord.id = ord_det.order_id JOIN discount as dis ON dis.id = ord.discount_id JOIN deliverer as del ON del.id = ord.deliverer_id JOIN customer as cus ON cus.id = ord.customer_id
